title: (Insert Rocky Theme Here) with Doug Mastriano and Jack Posobiec
itunes:title: (Insert Rocky Theme Here) with Doug Mastriano and Jack Posobiec
description:
Karl Rove is trying to sabotage Pennsylvania's Doug Mastriano by suggesting that Josh Shapiro is anti-crime. Mastriano joins Charlie to debunk that lie and show why only a Republican win will make Philly's streets safe again. Then, Jack Posobiec and Charlie discuss the single best development of Elon Musk's first day running Twitter: The firing of anti-white pro-censorship zealot Vijaya Gadde.
